title: WAQX-FM
text: WAQX-FM is an <a href="Alternative%20Rock">Alternative Rock</a> formatted <a href="Broadcasting">broadcast</a> <a href="radio%20station">radio station</a> licensed to <a href="Manlius%2C%20New%20York">Manlius, New York</a>, serving the <a href="Syracuse%2C%20New%20York">Syracuse, New York</a> market. WAQX-FM is owned and operated by <a href="Cumulus%20Media">Cumulus Media</a>.
